{"tid":649222,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"18歲仔遭狂斬命危","createTime":"2018-05-01T11:29:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-02T01:06:15.000Z","uid":25558,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"29703ddce9a49d3f1a134a59ea716fe6c764f066","tid":649222,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T11:29:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180501/20377880?_ga=2.12224564.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180501%2F20377880%3F_ga%3D2.12224564.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171&d=DsxdYVgv1v6SLJVdYobZ%2BIzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=7ab897d8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180501%2F20377880%3F_ga%3D2.12224564.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171&h=5cae665c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180501/20377880?_ga=2.12224564.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n18歲仔遭狂斬命危<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180501/large/0430laicwimg_0010.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180501%2Flarge%2F0430laicwimg_0010.jpg&h=c48c57f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■四漢扑爛的士車窗拖出青年狂斬，現場遺下大灘血迹。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】一名18歲青年昨凌晨與友人在元朗燒烤後，截乘的士期間遭4名大漢持鐵通及牛肉刀襲擊，更扑爛的士車窗拖出青年狂斬，事主身受重傷，經送院後情況危殆，警方初步相信案件涉及黑幫仇殺。<br />\n<br />\n重傷青年姓朱，前晚相約一批朋友在元朗山下路欖口村燒烤場燒烤，至昨凌晨3時許離開，事主先電召的士，然後與另一名16歲姓黃男友人步行50米至村口等候，此時突然有兩輛私家車馳至，4名大漢跳出車，分持牛肉刀及鐵通追向朱追斬，電召的士其後駛至，朱立即跳上的士，但兇徒追前扑爆車窗，將朱拖出狂斬，朱後腦及手臂中刀，惡煞事後登車逃去。<br />\n<br />\n朱頭手受創，由姓黃友人報警，送院治理後，情況危殆。警方兜截無果，消息指傷者有黑社會背景，案件交元朗警區反黑組接手追查。<br />\n<br />\n■記者黎志偉  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n五劫鳳姐　刀賊落網<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n港鐵荃灣綫訊號故障　金鐘站Not in Service"},{"pid":"c60451fd3e492c0fb2b32396b3da13d23990f4d3","tid":649222,"uid":120850,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T11:31:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 四個人點會斬唔死一條友<br />\n擺明靠嚇或者有春袋係一條友手"},{"pid":"c5351f9af3e57a078b4e5f8f799c7da7a2795a23","tid":649222,"uid":124277,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T11:32:05.000Z","msg":"得個dur dur 血..."},{"pid":"5cf5f48bd127b80e9ced64a3d93b587d37b2758f","tid":649222,"uid":20227,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T11:34:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8aef75ed89219b71a2ce3052eb43d4167eb9f609","tid":649222,"uid":85819,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T11:35:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5329d709924dfab5e6770e286aba00f02d6207a6","tid":649222,"uid":188,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T11:36:06.000Z","msg":"出得黎bbq預左死架喎<br />\n有得怨咩"},{"pid":"8ee436ecf1c2b8848a91e69af55d66e6640e4ae6","tid":649222,"uid":136455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T11:36:41.000Z","msg":"好有機會係蝻"},{"pid":"a05464500af465dfa41d5c66e21aeac4595b9436","tid":649222,"uid":113626,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T11:37:18.000Z","msg":"一睇就知咩丁權出事 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27e4347659f770d5754879e9707b85c473b961ef","tid":649222,"uid":7534,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T11:38:09.000Z","msg":"希望社會又少件垃圾啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddedc181c3f8281c1b9669ebc27f352a8144798f","tid":649222,"uid":135767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T13:36:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6a8640f6be7f1a8467d3ccb6718bf26c40a2ce49","tid":649222,"uid":116143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T13:39:38.000Z","msg":"出得黎行 預左條撚要還<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smi